OL,3,CHundreds of mobile phones crushed
OL,4,Cafter prison seizure
OL,6,FHundreds of mobile phones have been
OL,7,Fcrushed after they were seized from
OL,8,Fprison inmates.
OL,10,FThe devices, which police say were
OL,11,Fused to "arrange drug deals, weapon
OL,12,Fdrops and even plan violent attacks",
OL,13,Fwere being held illegally by prisoners
OL,14,Fat HMP Manchester.
OL,16,FOfficers from Greater Manchester
OL,17,FPolice (GMP) and His Majesty's Prison
OL,18,Fand Probation Service have seized and
OL,19,Fdestroyed more than 500 mobile phones,
OL,20,Felectronic devices and SIM cards which
OL,21,Fwere held by prisoners.
