OL,6,FGMP says the efforts form part of its
OL,7,Fwork in removing contraband that
OL,8,Fenables criminal networks to continue
OL,9,Foperating inside prison walls.
OL,11,FIt is the latest seizures of devices
OL,12,Fat HMP Manchester come as part of
OL,13,FOperation Sheriff, which is a multi-
OL,14,Fagency initiative targeting the
OL,15,Fmovement of drugs, weapons and illicit
OL,16,Fcontraband into prison facilities.
